    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all 5 COU operating points with mean absolute error of 0.043. The assessment team accepts the validation evidence as sufficient to support the COU decision, noting that the validation runs were executed under ansys-cfx-24-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 and that the released production version is ansys-cfx-24-build-2026-q1-build-7. The team has reviewed vendor release notes and concluded the patch-level difference is non-material to solver numerics; formal re-execution under the production build was not performed on the basis of this review.",
